  "time_ut": 1662292666,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc3 6\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0dad\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "If supported without politics, the country will be back to normal in 6 months",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former state minister Mr. Anuradha Jayaratne said that if the leader who took charge of the country to overcome the economic crisis of the country is supported without party color politics, the country's economy will be balanced within a short period of six months.",
        "The former state minister said that after participating as the chief guest in the softball cricket tournament held by the Nawalapitiya Police on (04) on the occasion of the 156th Police Day.",
        "Mr. Anuradha Jayaratne, the former Minister of State, who commented further, said that Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, who held the position of President of the country for a short period of two years, is a leader with a wealth of experience.",
        "Mr. Anuradha Jayaratne claims that in order to get those experiences from Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, he should be involved in active politics and give those experiences to the next generation.",
        "Mr. Anuradha Jayaratne further said that due to the increase in the price of fuel, the price of many essential food items has increased and has severely affected the people of the entire country, and it is only a short-term problem."
      ],
